      <title>由于汽车市场放缓，意法半导体下调了财年收入预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicro-cuts-fy-revenue-outlook-slowing-car-demand-bites-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲芯片制造商意法半导体周四下调了全年销售指引，这是最新一家因汽车制造商需求疲软以及笔记本电脑和手机公司订单进一步下降而苦苦挣扎的半导体公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicro-cuts-fy-revenue-outlook-slowing-car-demand-bites-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国巴黎银行利润高于预期，原因是成本下降和全球银行业</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bnp-paribas-profit-tops-estimates-lower-costs-global-banking-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国巴黎银行周四公布第一季度利润和收入下降，但超出了分析师的预期，因为费用降低和企业银行业务的强劲表现抵消了其他地区收入的持平或下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bnp-paribas-profit-tops-estimates-lower-costs-global-banking-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:13:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
