      <title>加拿大泰克资源公司第一季度利润低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/canadas-teck-resources-misses-first-quarter-profit-estimates-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大矿业公司泰克资源公司周四未能达到第一季度利润预期，部分原因是炼钢煤炭销量低迷和锌价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/canadas-teck-resources-misses-first-quarter-profit-estimates-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:11:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雀巢全面提价后销售业绩未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nestle-misses-quarterly-sales-estimates-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雀巢周四未达到第一季度有机销售增长预期，因为这家全球最大的包装食品公司提高了价格并减少了产品销量，尤其是在北美。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nestle-misses-quarterly-sales-estimates-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
