      <title>小米 SU7 汽车订单已超 7.5 万辆，6 月交付目标超 1 万辆</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-locks-over-75000-orders-su7-car-targets-over-10000-deliveries-june-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国智能手机制造商小米创始人雷军周四表示，截至 4 月 24 日，其运动型 SU7 电动轿车已锁定 75,723 辆订单，并计划在 6 月份交付超过 10,000 辆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-locks-over-75000-orders-su7-car-targets-over-10000-deliveries-june-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:19:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
